com.giannoules.proxstor.api

Class Location

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.giannoules.proxstor.api.Location

  • public class Location
extends Object
    ProxStor representation of a location. An location is the component which represents a place a ProxStor user can potentially be located. ProxStor defines some basic fields here, but primary importance is upon the type and identifier. This class is augmented with annotations identifying it for Java Architecture for XML Binding.
    Author:
    James Giannoules
